Package: frei0r-dev
Version: 2.3.2
Revision: 1
Description: Minimalistic plugin API for video effects
License: GPL
Maintainer: Hanspeter Niederstrasser <nieder@users.sourceforge.net>
BuildDepends: <<
	cairo (>= 1.12.8-1),
	cmake,
	fink-buildenv-modules,
	fink-package-precedence,
	fontconfig2-dev (>= 2.10.0-1),
	freetype219 (>= 2.12.1-4),
	libgavl1,
	pkgconfig,
	x11-dev
<<
BuildDependsOnly: true
Source: https://github.com/dyne/frei0r/archive/refs/tags/v%v.tar.gz
SourceRename: frei0r-%v.tar.gz
Source-Checksum: SHA256(304291e0ecb456a8b054fe04e14adc50ace54d0223b7b29165ff5343e820ef9d)
GCC: 4.0

CompileScript: <<
	#!/bin/sh -ev
	. %p/sbin/fink-buildenv-cmake.sh
	mkdir finkbuild
	pushd finkbuild
#			-DWITHOUT_GAVL=ON \
#			-DWITHOUT_CAIRO=ON \
		cmake $FINK_CMAKE_ARGS \
			-DDOXYGEN_EXECUTABLE=NOT_FOUND \
			-DWITHOUT_OPENCV=ON \
			-LAH \
			..
		make -w
	popd
	fink-package-precedence --prohibit-bdep frei0r-dev --depfile-ext='\.d' .
<<
InstallScript: <<
	cd finkbuild; make install DESTDIR=%d
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog README.md
Splitoff: <<
	Package: frei0r
	Depends: <<
		cairo-shlibs (>= 1.12.8-1),
		libgavl1-shlibs
	<<
	Description: Minimalistic API video effects plugins
	DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog README.md
	Files: lib/frei0r-1
<<
Homepage: http://frei0r.dyne.org/
DescDetail: <<
Frei0r is a minimalistic plugin API for video sources and filters. The 
behaviour of the effects can be controlled from the host by simple 
parameters. The intent is to solve the recurring reimplementation or 
adaptation issue of standard effects.
<<
